metadata.name: Fortune Tiger #1
metadata.description: The Fortune Tigers are a Chinese Zodiac based and Lunar New Year themed collection of 10,000 felines living on the Ethereum blockchain. This lucky token acts as an entry ticket to participate in the fun and exciting "perpetual raffle giveaway system" for ETH prizes and more. The upcoming year of 2022 is the year of the Tiger so this token is intended to grant prosperity and wealth. Remember - fortune favors the bold!
